WEBVTT

1
00:00:41.250 --> 00:00:46.005
INTERNATIONAL WATERS
CENTRAL AMERICA

2
00:00:57.183 --> 00:00:58.684
How's the wound. B?

3
00:00:59.268 --> 00:01:00.936
I have to rest.

4
00:01:01.020 --> 00:01:03.147
Right. Be careful going down the stairs.

5
00:01:05.858 --> 00:01:07.193
Welcome aboard.

6
00:01:07.818 --> 00:01:09.737
We're happy to be back.

7
00:01:10.237 --> 00:01:12.531
Do you have any snacks?

8
00:01:15.284 --> 00:01:17.495
Really? Do you have first aid?

9
00:01:17.578 --> 00:01:19.330
He has a serious wound.

10
00:01:21.957 --> 00:01:23.459
And a place to rest?

11
00:01:28.047 --> 00:01:29.423
No? Okay.

12
00:01:30.633 --> 00:01:31.634
Hello.

13
00:01:48.317 --> 00:01:49.693
Zero. We...

14
00:01:53.030 --> 00:01:55.991
Let's go back to Costa Verde...

15
00:01:56.075 --> 00:01:57.576
... ERGI terrorists.

16
00:02:20.307 --> 00:02:22.184
I'm on my way. Are you listening?

17
00:02:25.312 --> 00:02:26.814
Can you hear me?

18
00:02:29.191 --> 00:02:30.359
This can't be good.

19
00:02:30.442 --> 00:02:33.571
If you don't listen to me... Godspeed!

20
00:02:34.321 --> 00:02:35.948
Who the hell is coming?

21
00:02:36.031 --> 00:02:36.949
Death.

22
00:02:37.032 --> 00:02:39.451
Courtesy of Roman Díaz.

23
00:02:56.844 --> 00:02:58.095
Shit!

24
00:02:58.971 --> 00:03:00.472
I can't see anything.

25
00:03:03.309 --> 00:03:06.103
Turn off the engine.
Look for a flare gun.

26
00:04:41.573 --> 00:04:44.243
Half dead and blind.
I think you'll get the engine right.

27
00:04:48.831 --> 00:04:50.082
It's a lot of blood. B.

28
00:04:50.165 --> 00:04:53.043
Can we take a break. please? Come on!

29
00:05:15.482 --> 00:05:17.609
- Do you have the flare gun?
- Yes. sir.

30
00:05:18.485 --> 00:05:19.862
Get ready to shoot.

31
00:05:20.654 --> 00:05:21.655
Shoot!

32
00:05:31.206 --> 00:05:33.000
Nice shot. B! Nice shot. B!

33
00:05:36.086 --> 00:05:37.379
Yes!

34
00:05:39.465 --> 00:05:40.466
Holy shit!

35
00:05:43.802 --> 00:05:44.803
B?

36
00:05:46.847 --> 00:05:49.183
Hey! Stay with me. brother.

37
00:05:49.933 --> 00:05:50.934
Come on.

38
00:05:52.436 --> 00:05:53.437
Shit!

39
00:05:54.730 --> 00:05:55.981
Hey!

40
00:05:56.065 --> 00:05:57.149
Hang in there.

41
00:06:22.925 --> 00:06:24.426
Ezekiel Rosenberg.

42
00:06:25.344 --> 00:06:26.762
You have exactly five minutes

43
00:06:26.845 --> 00:06:29.389
to tell me
what happened in Costa Verde.

44
00:06:32.601 --> 00:06:34.770
Colonel Stone sent us

45
00:06:34.853 --> 00:06:36.355
to help with a mission.

46
00:06:36.438 --> 00:06:37.523
We suffered casualties.

47
00:06:39.691 --> 00:06:40.734
Many casualties.

48
00:06:41.777 --> 00:06:44.780
But four of us left
with information we sent

49
00:06:44.863 --> 00:06:47.533
to a satellite.
which broadcast them to the agencies.

50
00:06:47.616 --> 00:06:49.284
The information we collect...

51
00:06:49.368 --> 00:06:50.869
Where's Brandon Beckett?

52
00:06:52.454 --> 00:06:53.831
Is he still alive?

53
00:06:57.417 --> 00:07:00.671
We encountered some problems
during our extraction.

54
00:07:01.296 --> 00:07:02.297
Problems?

55
00:07:03.257 --> 00:07:06.301
Its specificity is... inspiring.

56
00:07:07.219 --> 00:07:09.179
What the hell happened there?

57
00:07:11.014 --> 00:07:13.642
We were picked up by friends
of our former commander.

58
00:07:13.725 --> 00:07:16.687
When rescue didn't call.
they sent a helicopter.

59
00:07:17.312 --> 00:07:19.148
He took Brandon to a safe place.

60
00:07:19.231 --> 00:07:23.235
After that. my orders were to
return to ERGI headquarters for a meeting.

61
00:07:23.318 --> 00:07:25.571
Then I received an encrypted message.

62
00:07:25.654 --> 00:07:28.448
presumably yours.
telling me to come here.

63
00:07:31.910 --> 00:07:35.664
It's your turn.
What the hell am I doing here?

64
00:07:40.878 --> 00:07:45.799
My name is Devon Frost.
I'm a cleaner. a supplier.

65
00:07:46.425 --> 00:07:49.386
And I was tasked with dismantling ERGI.

66
00:07:50.512 --> 00:07:51.847
I'll update it.

67
00:07:52.389 --> 00:07:55.851
The prime minister of the country he
has just fled says that the US

68
00:07:55.934 --> 00:08:00.397
infiltrated ERGI in Costa Verde
to dismantle his political power.

69
00:08:00.480 --> 00:08:02.441
It's a typical Soviet move.

70
00:08:02.524 --> 00:08:04.651
You know. saying that the US

71
00:08:04.735 --> 00:08:06.361
are invading their territory.

72
00:08:06.445 --> 00:08:10.574
So. to avoid a major
international incident.

73
00:08:10.657 --> 00:08:14.578
the CIA hired an external
to deal with the situation.

74
00:08:14.661 --> 00:08:17.122
so that you don't even suspect it.

75
00:08:18.415 --> 00:08:21.084
Nod your head
if you're following along.

76
00:08:22.669 --> 00:08:25.505
In short. all
paper and digital

77
00:08:25.589 --> 00:08:28.383
that the Global Response
and Intelligence Team existed

78
00:08:28.467 --> 00:08:29.968
have been erased from the planet.

79
00:08:31.053 --> 00:08:33.263
ERGI no longer exists.

80
00:08:36.308 --> 00:08:38.352
But here's the problem. Ezekiel.

81
00:08:39.770 --> 00:08:41.021
Your team is on the run.

82
00:08:41.647 --> 00:08:42.648
They're hidden.

83
00:08:43.357 --> 00:08:48.028
"The Colonel". Gabriel Stone. Yuki Mifune.
also known as Lady Death.

84
00:08:48.111 --> 00:08:50.280
Peter Stolnitz. or Pete Intelligence.

85
00:08:50.364 --> 00:08:56.119
and the rest of your bunch of misfits
with goofy nicknames are gone.

86
00:08:56.203 --> 00:08:57.871
since the Costa Verde mess.

87
00:08:59.373 --> 00:09:00.374
It's just you.

88
00:09:01.708 --> 00:09:05.504
He was the only one foolish enough
to return to the United States.

89
00:09:09.174 --> 00:09:12.511
Last chance.
Where's Brandon Beckett?

90
00:09:15.472 --> 00:09:16.473
Time's up.

91
00:09:19.810 --> 00:09:22.938
Ezekiel Rosenberg.
is being held under the Patriot Act.

92
00:09:24.731 --> 00:09:27.192
The Patriot Act? That's for terrorists.

93
00:09:27.276 --> 00:09:30.028
That's what they call it now.
Zero. terrorist.

94
00:10:03.395 --> 00:10:04.521
Hello. Zero.

95
00:10:07.107 --> 00:10:08.108
My son?

96
00:10:08.650 --> 00:10:13.447
SNIPER: NO NATION

97
00:10:14.114 --> 00:10:15.324
Citizens of Costa Verde.

98
00:10:17.117 --> 00:10:20.912
I have proof that the ERGI
team from the US CIA

99
00:10:21.538 --> 00:10:25.542
illegally entered Costa Verde
and killed a government supplier.

100
00:10:25.625 --> 00:10:28.754
along with more than 100 soldiers.

101
00:10:28.837 --> 00:10:33.216
This unprecedented act of terror
will not go unanswered...

102
00:10:33.300 --> 00:10:37.179
The prime minister's nephew
was killed helping these foreigners.

103
00:10:37.846 --> 00:10:40.390
The United States denies it completely

104
00:10:40.474 --> 00:10:43.685
any involvement
in the incident in Costa Verde.

105
00:10:44.853 --> 00:10:47.731
Let's not forget that the
of the Prime Minister. Bruno Díaz.

106
00:10:47.814 --> 00:10:50.275
was assassinated by a sniper
hired by Americans.

107
00:10:51.276 --> 00:10:55.072
Prime Minister Díaz's accusations
are unfounded and absurd.

108
00:10:55.155 --> 00:10:58.408
And the American marine
Brandon Beckett not a suspect?

109
00:10:58.492 --> 00:11:01.036
No. Brandon Beckett
didn't kill Bruno Díaz.

110
00:11:01.119 --> 00:11:03.705
He was cleared
and those responsible were caught.

111
00:11:03.789 --> 00:11:05.874
thanks in part to him and his father.

112
00:11:05.957 --> 00:11:08.001
I smell a cover-up. It always has.

113
00:11:08.585 --> 00:11:12.130
It's not the first time that Costa Verde
has tried to distract the world

114
00:11:12.214 --> 00:11:14.132
poverty. corruption

115
00:11:14.216 --> 00:11:16.802
and brutality
within its borders.

116
00:11:17.344 --> 00:11:20.472
This is the latest attempt by the US

117
00:11:20.555 --> 00:11:24.601
to interfere and control
our internal affairs.

118
00:11:24.684 --> 00:11:28.271
In short. the Americans are helping
the so-called Phoenix Rebels

119
00:11:28.355 --> 00:11:30.982
causing disturbances in Costa Verde.

120
00:11:31.066 --> 00:11:32.067
PRIME MINISTER

121
00:11:32.150 --> 00:11:34.027
We can't allow this any longer!

122
00:11:34.111 --> 00:11:37.823
Their violence will spread across the
border to the streets of Tierra Nueva.

123
00:11:37.906 --> 00:11:39.282
As for ERGI.

124
00:11:39.366 --> 00:11:42.332
the Global Response and Intelligence Team

125
00:11:42.411 --> 00:11:45.414
is an enemy of the United States of America.

126
00:11:45.497 --> 00:11:49.793
All those involved in this
false flag terrorist organization

127
00:11:49.876 --> 00:11:53.922
will be persecuted and face
the consequences of this operation.

128
00:11:54.005 --> 00:11:55.882
Consider yourselves warned. America.

129
00:11:55.966 --> 00:11:59.594
They will answer for this betrayal!

130
00:12:00.887 --> 00:12:02.055
Thank you.

131
00:12:06.184 --> 00:12:09.312
HIDING PLACE OF THE IRON LEGION
EAST AFRICA

132
00:12:10.981 --> 00:12:11.982
Stupid.

133
00:12:15.318 --> 00:12:16.319
Come on. man!

134
00:12:29.791 --> 00:12:32.210
Listen.

135
00:12:35.338 --> 00:12:37.883
For the right price. you can find anyone.

136
00:12:37.966 --> 00:12:40.510
The prime minister's navy
didn't stop Beckett

137
00:12:40.594 --> 00:12:42.971
- and ERGI to flee the country.
- Beckett?

138
00:12:45.015 --> 00:12:46.057
Father or son?

139
00:12:47.476 --> 00:12:49.102
What do you mean. Brandon Beckett? Brandon Beckett.

140
00:12:51.104 --> 00:12:55.442
The Beckett's are the best snipers
on the planet and you did

141
00:12:55.525 --> 00:12:57.235
son an enemy.

142
00:12:59.946 --> 00:13:05.827
I don't care about his reputation.
Find him and bring him to Roman. Alive.

143
00:13:05.911 --> 00:13:09.164
Your boss wants to use you
as a political chess piece.

144
00:13:09.247 --> 00:13:13.210
I have a television. Mr. Cabrera.
I understand the current situation. Yes.

145
00:13:13.960 --> 00:13:17.714
Then you will know that ERGI
is no longer welcome in the United States.

146
00:13:17.797 --> 00:13:19.216
so it's not there.

147
00:13:19.925 --> 00:13:23.678
Don't tell me. That's why
we're going to start in Costa Verde.

148
00:13:25.931 --> 00:13:27.182
Are you coming here?

149
00:13:27.974 --> 00:13:32.687
ERGI was working
with the Phoenix Rebellion in your country.

150
00:13:32.771 --> 00:13:37.025
If I start killing rebels. I'll end up
finding someone they like.

151
00:13:39.277 --> 00:13:41.238
Which will bring Brandon to us.

152
00:13:41.321 --> 00:13:42.989
Killing a Beckett will be fun.

153
00:13:43.073 --> 00:13:45.242
And you. have my money ready.

154
00:13:45.992 --> 00:13:47.202
Of course.

155
00:13:47.285 --> 00:13:49.246
We have cryptocurrencies for this...

156
00:13:49.329 --> 00:13:53.917
No. I don't want cryptocurrencies
from Costa Verde.

157
00:13:54.000 --> 00:13:55.669
I want real money.

158
00:13:55.752 --> 00:13:58.630
I want a million up front.
And I want five million on delivery.

159
00:13:58.713 --> 00:13:59.714
Don't worry.

160
00:14:01.925 --> 00:14:03.260
You'll get your money.

161
00:14:03.343 --> 00:14:06.596
I've been burned too many times
by customers who don't pay.

162
00:14:06.680 --> 00:14:07.973
And if you don't pay...

163
00:14:09.057 --> 00:14:12.185
... will feel the consequences
of the Iron Legion.

164
00:14:12.269 --> 00:14:15.188
- Kruger!
- Call me when it's done.

165
00:14:20.235 --> 00:14:23.530
DEACTIVATED MILITARY BASE
TIERRA NUEVA - CENTRAL AMERICA

166
00:14:27.284 --> 00:14:30.579
Roman has the entire Costa Verde
in a media blackout.

167
00:14:30.662 --> 00:14:32.747
No news in or out
or social networks.

168
00:14:32.831 --> 00:14:35.584
But it seems that some rebels
have occasionally broken

169
00:14:35.667 --> 00:14:37.168
the firewalls and spread the truth.

170
00:14:38.003 --> 00:14:40.964
There are some great Roman Díaz memes out there.

171
00:14:41.047 --> 00:14:43.883
There's one with a cat. a can opener and...
You'll have to see.

172
00:14:43.967 --> 00:14:45.010
Pete Intelligence

173
00:14:48.179 --> 00:14:51.182
I'd love to know that the hackers
are getting through.

174
00:14:55.228 --> 00:14:59.399
Do you think Díaz knows that his nephew
died trying to stop him?

175
00:14:59.482 --> 00:15:01.818
He doesn't strike me as a family man.

176
00:15:04.446 --> 00:15:09.367
Roman said that any
agent found in his country

177
00:15:09.451 --> 00:15:10.827
will be executed.

178
00:15:12.203 --> 00:15:14.372
I'm worried about Zondi.
Did you find him?

179
00:15:15.248 --> 00:15:18.084
I'm getting closer.
You'll have news soon.

180
00:15:19.294 --> 00:15:20.962
If anyone can do it. it's you.

181
00:15:21.921 --> 00:15:25.342
Brandon. if you need any help.
let us know and we'll be there.

182
00:15:28.553 --> 00:15:32.807
Thanks. but... it's too dangerous.

183
00:15:34.351 --> 00:15:36.770
Yuki can't enter Costa Verde.

184
00:15:37.562 --> 00:15:40.273
I would literally be chased
by everyone.

185
00:15:41.524 --> 00:15:44.861
Keep a low profile.
Keep Yuki and the colonel hidden. will you?

186
00:15:44.944 --> 00:15:46.946
- I'm counting on you. buddy.
- I'm counting on you. buddy.

187
00:15:51.117 --> 00:15:52.410
I have to go.

188
00:15:53.244 --> 00:15:54.871
- Stay safe.
- Be careful.

189
00:16:04.506 --> 00:16:05.924
"There's a thunderstorm coming."

190
00:16:07.884 --> 00:16:09.761
"Then you'd better get your boots..."

191
00:16:09.844 --> 00:16:11.805
"... and go dancing in the rain."

192
00:16:14.474 --> 00:16:17.352
Shooting instructor. sir. What are you doing here?

193
00:16:17.936 --> 00:16:19.187
I've come to see my son.

194
00:16:26.361 --> 00:16:27.487
Devon Frost.

195
00:16:27.570 --> 00:16:30.281
I was your father's pointer on a mission

196
00:16:30.365 --> 00:16:32.075
when we went to Costa Verde.

197
00:16:33.618 --> 00:16:35.245
It's a pleasure to meet you. sir.

198
00:16:35.995 --> 00:16:37.539
This is a good one.

199
00:16:38.832 --> 00:16:42.085
So you came all this way
just to escort us home?

200
00:16:45.130 --> 00:16:46.548
He's not coming back.

201
00:16:48.049 --> 00:16:50.719
You are a man without a nation. Brandon Beckett.

202
00:16:51.511 --> 00:16:52.512
What?

203
00:17:00.687 --> 00:17:01.938
Can't we go back?

204
00:17:02.021 --> 00:17:03.356
Believe me. I tried.

205
00:17:03.440 --> 00:17:05.525
After all we've done for the country.

206
00:17:06.735 --> 00:17:09.404
Brandon. can you give him
some time to calm down?

207
00:17:10.613 --> 00:17:13.116
The President and the State Department

208
00:17:13.199 --> 00:17:17.704
are trying to calm this down
to avoid chaos in the region.

209
00:17:17.787 --> 00:17:19.205
You've seen this before.

210
00:17:20.165 --> 00:17:21.499
You know how it works.

211
00:17:25.253 --> 00:17:26.921
Should I keep hiding here?

212
00:17:27.547 --> 00:17:29.632
We can stay as long as we need to.

213
00:17:29.716 --> 00:17:31.801
There are still guards patrolling here.

214
00:17:31.885 --> 00:17:33.261
Was this the agreed place?

215
00:17:33.344 --> 00:17:35.138
Yes. This is where we should

216
00:17:35.221 --> 00:17:38.641
bring in the prisoners Kovalov and Maxim
before our mission fails.

217
00:17:38.725 --> 00:17:39.726
You know what?

218
00:17:40.226 --> 00:17:41.227
You'd better go.

219
00:17:42.645 --> 00:17:45.565
Before that revolution
crosses the border here.

220
00:17:47.859 --> 00:17:48.902
Roman doesn't invade.

221
00:17:49.736 --> 00:17:52.947
He's still licking his wounds
for breaking up his militia.

222
00:17:53.031 --> 00:17:55.200
What's more. it has no allied countries

223
00:17:55.283 --> 00:17:59.329
and will not go to war
with Tierra Nueva and the US alone.

224
00:18:00.413 --> 00:18:03.917
So you're screwed
if you do it or not. aren't you?

225
00:18:06.169 --> 00:18:08.087
What do you suggest I do?

226
00:18:08.171 --> 00:18:09.172
We fight.

227
00:18:09.923 --> 00:18:10.924
We fight.

228
00:18:11.466 --> 00:18:12.717
As always. B.

229
00:18:14.719 --> 00:18:17.055
We helped clean up this mess
in Costa Verde.

230
00:18:17.138 --> 00:18:18.723
Zero. take it easy.

231
00:18:19.182 --> 00:18:20.725
No country supports you.

232
00:18:20.809 --> 00:18:22.685
They stay here. discreet and safe.

233
00:18:25.146 --> 00:18:29.526
For God's sake.
you barely made it back alive.

234
00:18:30.318 --> 00:18:31.361
What do you have to do?

235
00:18:31.444 --> 00:18:33.571
You have to come with me to South America.

236
00:18:34.155 --> 00:18:38.284
I have many friends and good contacts.

237
00:18:38.368 --> 00:18:39.828
It's up to you. B.

238
00:18:45.375 --> 00:18:48.044
We should help the Phoenix Rebellion
in any way we can.

239
00:18:48.127 --> 00:18:50.630
but without entering their country.

240
00:18:50.713 --> 00:18:54.592
If we kill Prime Minister Díaz.
things will work out for us too.

241
00:18:56.135 --> 00:18:57.178
They win and we win.

242
00:18:57.262 --> 00:18:58.680
That's a lot of ifs.

243
00:19:02.141 --> 00:19:03.685
We need to talk to Zondi.

244
00:19:05.103 --> 00:19:06.604
How did they find us?

245
00:19:07.188 --> 00:19:10.608
Pete Intelligence managed to break
the firewalls and connect us all.

246
00:19:10.692 --> 00:19:12.819
Tell us what's happening in Costa Verde.

247
00:19:12.902 --> 00:19:15.238
Roman has a secret project
in the mountains...

248
00:19:15.321 --> 00:19:16.865
PHOENIX REBEL BASE
GREEN COAST - CENTRAL AMERICA

249
00:19:16.948 --> 00:19:18.283
... along the border.

250
00:19:18.992 --> 00:19:21.578
I orchestrated a squad to investigate.

251
00:19:21.661 --> 00:19:25.331
I stayed in Costa Verde
to complete what we all started.

252
00:19:26.040 --> 00:19:29.210
And when they get here.
no one will stop us.

253
00:19:33.631 --> 00:19:35.341
We can't go back there.

254
00:19:37.093 --> 00:19:41.222
If they catch us. we risk
giving Roman the excuse he needs

255
00:19:41.306 --> 00:19:43.141
to create an international incident.

256
00:19:45.393 --> 00:19:48.271
I heard the news. You're a soldier without a country.

257
00:19:48.354 --> 00:19:51.065
but we can find a way
for this to work.

258
00:19:51.149 --> 00:19:54.944
It's not safe for any American citizen
to be there right now.

259
00:19:55.445 --> 00:19:59.157
The President asked all expatriates
and humanitarian workers

260
00:19:59.282 --> 00:20:02.035
to leave.
The situation is a powder keg.

261
00:20:02.118 --> 00:20:04.746
We can help in another way.
We meet

262
00:20:04.829 --> 00:20:07.081
at the border with supplies.

263
00:20:07.165 --> 00:20:09.667
We don't need food
or toilet paper.

264
00:20:11.669 --> 00:20:13.504
We need soldiers!

265
00:20:13.588 --> 00:20:16.591
We need the best sniper in the world
to fight by our side.

266
00:20:17.884 --> 00:20:21.346
Zondi. the supplies
we're talking about are weapons.

267
00:20:21.930 --> 00:20:24.807
My contacts in Tierra Nueva
have a lot of weapons

268
00:20:24.891 --> 00:20:27.268
that are being brought to us
at the moment.

269
00:20:29.646 --> 00:20:32.482
They bring us weapons
to fight this battle alone.

270
00:20:33.441 --> 00:20:35.735
They won't come back to help us. Angel.

271
00:20:38.905 --> 00:20:39.906
Angel?

272
00:20:40.907 --> 00:20:42.951
Gentlemen. I understand your position.

273
00:20:43.701 --> 00:20:44.869
But elections are coming

274
00:20:44.953 --> 00:20:46.496
and Roman is the only one in the bulletin.

275
00:20:47.163 --> 00:20:48.998
No one will challenge him.

276
00:20:49.082 --> 00:20:51.918
We have to eliminate
Roman's influence now.

277
00:20:52.001 --> 00:20:54.587
so that the people can
vote for a new leader.

278
00:20:54.671 --> 00:20:57.131
Otherwise. we won't stop
his power in Costa Verde.

279
00:20:58.633 --> 00:21:00.635
You should be in South Africa
with your daughter.

280
00:21:01.302 --> 00:21:02.720
Why are you in Costa Verde?

281
00:21:04.597 --> 00:21:07.266
Modise wouldn't want
me to leave Zondi.

282
00:21:08.059 --> 00:21:11.354
Angel. is there anything else going on?

283
00:21:12.021 --> 00:21:14.232
Things have gotten worse here.

284
00:21:15.858 --> 00:21:20.822
Their tactics have become
more brutal. uncompromising.

285
00:21:22.991 --> 00:21:26.786
So you're going to meet us
at the border with weapons. yes?

286
00:21:28.663 --> 00:21:29.747
We'll talk more about it later.

287
00:21:30.331 --> 00:21:33.292
But the clock is ticking.
We have to move forward.

288
00:21:38.339 --> 00:21:41.217
I know it doesn't make sense
not to go back to Costa Verde to fight.

289
00:21:43.344 --> 00:21:44.554
Know that I support you.

290
00:21:47.849 --> 00:21:50.977
You've become a leader. Zondi.
I'm proud of you.

291
00:21:54.689 --> 00:21:56.107
Staying was the right decision.

292
00:21:57.859 --> 00:22:00.028
I've been using the lessons you taught me.

293
00:22:00.111 --> 00:22:03.990
Twelve deaths. not counting the twenty
of our battle together

294
00:22:04.073 --> 00:22:05.658
in the Kovalov complex.

295
00:22:07.702 --> 00:22:12.040
Don't become your death toll.
I've never seen that route end well.

296
00:22:15.293 --> 00:22:17.253
I long to fight alongside you again.

297
00:22:18.755 --> 00:22:19.756
Until that day.

298
00:22:20.923 --> 00:22:23.092
I will continue to lead here alone.

299
00:22:26.179 --> 00:22:27.346
Goodbye.

300
00:22:32.602 --> 00:22:35.229
Frost. I'll send you the coordinates

301
00:22:35.313 --> 00:22:36.981
to the place of delivery.

302
00:22:37.065 --> 00:22:38.441
I'm waiting. Katrina.

303
00:22:40.651 --> 00:22:42.487
Why haven't we done this before?

304
00:22:42.570 --> 00:22:44.489
Because I've seen you fight.

305
00:22:44.572 --> 00:22:46.282
You're a bit...

306
00:22:46.365 --> 00:22:47.533
Aggressive?

307
00:22:48.117 --> 00:22:51.537
I was going to say "unbalanced".
but "aggressive" sounds better.

308
00:22:53.331 --> 00:22:54.332
Well done.

309
00:22:55.750 --> 00:22:56.834
Show me what you've got.

310
00:23:22.610 --> 00:23:24.320
- That was good.
- Are you all right?

311
00:23:27.865 --> 00:23:28.866
Commander Zondi.

312
00:23:28.950 --> 00:23:29.951
PHOENIX REBEL BASE
GREEN COAST

313
00:23:30.034 --> 00:23:31.869
Will the Americans join us?

314
00:23:31.953 --> 00:23:34.664
No. Lorenzo. but they will supply us with weapons.

315
00:23:34.747 --> 00:23:37.250
It's not the answer I wanted.
but we accept everything.

316
00:23:37.333 --> 00:23:38.835
Our soldiers are ready.

317
00:23:38.918 --> 00:23:41.629
Start loading your gear.
We leave at sunset.

318
00:23:41.712 --> 00:23:43.840
Take your night vision.
We're going to need it.

319
00:23:43.923 --> 00:23:45.299
- Angel?
- Yes?

320
00:23:45.383 --> 00:23:48.553
I want Lorenzo to lead Team C.
You take B.

321
00:23:48.636 --> 00:23:50.054
I lead Squad A.

322
00:23:50.721 --> 00:23:52.557
We have to be prepared for anything.

323
00:23:52.640 --> 00:23:55.226
I don't want anything to go wrong
when we arrive.

324
00:23:55.309 --> 00:23:56.769
We have to make sure that...

325
00:24:00.189 --> 00:24:01.983
Let's go!

326
00:24:11.450 --> 00:24:13.911
Let's burn ammunition!

327
00:25:47.672 --> 00:25:48.673
So?

328
00:25:51.259 --> 00:25:52.343
Have we ruined everything?

329
00:25:53.261 --> 00:25:54.553
The last mission?

330
00:25:55.596 --> 00:25:56.806
Just look at the result.

331
00:25:57.473 --> 00:26:01.394
People like Stone.
Pete Intelligence. Yuki.

332
00:26:01.477 --> 00:26:03.104
now they're all on the run and...

333
00:26:03.187 --> 00:26:05.022
We've completed the mission. B.

334
00:26:05.856 --> 00:26:07.984
And the information we brought
gave good results.

335
00:26:08.067 --> 00:26:10.403
And we kept
a deadly weapon away from Roman.

336
00:26:11.362 --> 00:26:13.364
This situation will be resolved. You'll see.

337
00:26:14.282 --> 00:26:15.449
We'll be back soon.

338
00:26:18.286 --> 00:26:19.412
I don't know. man.

339
00:26:24.625 --> 00:26:26.877
I feel most at home
when I'm on a mission.

340
00:26:28.129 --> 00:26:31.090
When I go back to my house.
I'm a stranger.

341
00:26:32.258 --> 00:26:34.343
You can't go near anyone.

342
00:26:35.553 --> 00:26:37.054
because you're always leaving.

343
00:26:37.805 --> 00:26:39.849
And you can't say where you're going.
because...

344
00:26:39.932 --> 00:26:44.729
That's why Shelly is my ex-wife.
We never managed to plan a life together.

345
00:26:45.730 --> 00:26:48.733
"I'm sorry. darling. I can't go
to the Johnsons' barbecue

346
00:26:48.816 --> 00:26:51.902
because I have to stop a dictator
from starting World War III.

347
00:26:52.653 --> 00:26:54.572
But eat potato salad for me."

348
00:26:55.156 --> 00:26:57.616
Anyway. what can you do?

349
00:26:58.617 --> 00:27:00.661
Work calls. we answer.

350
00:27:00.745 --> 00:27:02.246
Come on. let's go.

351
00:28:24.787 --> 00:28:27.581
Angel. get as many
people as possible.

352
00:28:29.625 --> 00:28:30.626
Go!

353
00:28:52.148 --> 00:28:53.732
Oh. shit. It was in your wound.

354
00:29:00.698 --> 00:29:03.033
Come on. man! It wasn't cool!

355
00:29:03.617 --> 00:29:05.202
I thought you were hurt.

356
00:29:05.870 --> 00:29:07.455
Why are you playing with my emotions?

357
00:29:08.539 --> 00:29:10.416
You told me to do my best.

358
00:29:10.499 --> 00:29:12.460
- Jesus!
- Brandon. Zero.

359
00:29:13.335 --> 00:29:15.087
There was an attack.

360
00:29:37.318 --> 00:29:39.403
VIDEO CALL
ON

361
00:29:59.840 --> 00:30:01.342
Did you enjoy the show. Brandon?

362
00:30:05.137 --> 00:30:06.305
It's the next one.

363
00:30:07.348 --> 00:30:08.474
MISSED CONNECTION

364
00:30:11.227 --> 00:30:12.478
Safe bridge.

365
00:30:15.523 --> 00:30:18.150
- Useless.
- What do you want now. bitch?

366
00:30:18.776 --> 00:30:21.654
You're just breathing
because I need live bait.

367
00:30:22.196 --> 00:30:23.280
Otherwise. I'd open you up

368
00:30:24.365 --> 00:30:26.492
and remove your organs
in alphabetical order.

369
00:30:28.410 --> 00:30:30.996
Uncuff me.
Let's see "who" cuts whom.

370
00:30:34.250 --> 00:30:35.251
"Who".

371
00:30:38.128 --> 00:30:40.756
Who. Who would cut whom.

372
00:30:42.258 --> 00:30:44.843
If you want to threaten me.
at least get your grammar right.

373
00:30:48.138 --> 00:30:50.599
The body count is 50.
So far.

374
00:30:55.062 --> 00:30:56.438
Want to know why?

375
00:30:57.940 --> 00:30:59.275
Brandon Beckett.

376
00:31:01.652 --> 00:31:04.405
Beckett wants you dead. All of you.

377
00:31:05.864 --> 00:31:09.076
This is proof that ERGI
was in Costa Verde.

378
00:31:09.159 --> 00:31:11.704
When he passed the firewall
to call you.

379
00:31:11.787 --> 00:31:13.956
we traced that call back here.

380
00:31:17.084 --> 00:31:19.712
Talking to him
was your death sentence.

381
00:31:21.755 --> 00:31:23.007
And he knew it.

382
00:31:36.395 --> 00:31:39.898
Give me Brandon Beckett
and I'll give you an honorable death.

383
00:31:47.865 --> 00:31:49.658
I was hoping you'd say that.

384
00:31:51.076 --> 00:31:52.077
Legions!

385
00:31:54.163 --> 00:31:55.164
Let's go!

386
00:31:58.042 --> 00:32:01.670
- Come here. damn it!
- Come here!

387
00:32:05.424 --> 00:32:08.135
Come on. follow me.

388
00:32:08.886 --> 00:32:12.014
I was on a video call
with Katrina when they arrived.

389
00:32:12.848 --> 00:32:15.517
More than 50 Phoenix Rebels
were killed in the attack.

390
00:32:15.601 --> 00:32:17.353
Three were taken hostage.

391
00:32:17.436 --> 00:32:19.688
Lorenzo. Angel and Zondi.

392
00:32:19.772 --> 00:32:20.898
Holy shit!

393
00:32:21.398 --> 00:32:23.776
- But are they alive?
- As far as we know.

394
00:32:25.986 --> 00:32:27.196
Who are these guys?

395
00:32:29.490 --> 00:32:30.616
They're called the Iron Legion.

396
00:32:33.035 --> 00:32:36.580
They are a lethal private mercenary group
that operates without limitations.

397
00:32:36.664 --> 00:32:38.832
These are the anti-ERGI types.

398
00:32:38.916 --> 00:32:42.628
A collection of wanted agents
and ex-militants dishonorably discharged

399
00:32:42.711 --> 00:32:44.421
from all over the world.

400
00:32:44.505 --> 00:32:47.174
Their only loyalty? Whoever hires them.

401
00:32:48.217 --> 00:32:49.927
The leader is this gem. Killian Kruger.

402
00:32:50.010 --> 00:32:51.512
KNOWN AS

403
00:32:52.763 --> 00:32:54.723
Former South African
Forces

404
00:32:54.807 --> 00:32:56.809
who became a murderer and an anarchist.

405
00:32:56.892 --> 00:33:00.354
The Special Forces expelled him
when the colonel considered him "unstable".

406
00:33:00.437 --> 00:33:03.357
In response. he beat the colonel
to death with a golf club.

407
00:33:03.440 --> 00:33:05.651
then folded the
in the golf bag

408
00:33:05.734 --> 00:33:07.861
and sent it to the Brigadier General.

409
00:33:10.030 --> 00:33:12.825
The truth is that I've known about the Legion for years.

410
00:33:12.908 --> 00:33:16.370
They never stay long enough
in one place to be located.

411
00:33:16.453 --> 00:33:18.747
My sources say
that Roman's head of security

412
00:33:18.831 --> 00:33:19.873
Francisco Cabrera.

413
00:33:19.957 --> 00:33:23.544
hired them with the aim of
to eliminate the Phoenix Rebels.

414
00:33:25.754 --> 00:33:28.090
And to find you. Brandon.

415
00:33:29.925 --> 00:33:31.260
How did you find the rebels?

416
00:33:35.723 --> 00:33:36.932
Us.

417
00:33:38.934 --> 00:33:42.646
When Smart Pete broke
Roman's media blackout.

418
00:33:42.730 --> 00:33:46.150
the video call was traced
to the location of the rebels.

419
00:33:46.233 --> 00:33:48.277
The Legion just isn't on our doorstep

420
00:33:48.360 --> 00:33:50.529
because the signal could only be traced
in Costa Verde.

421
00:33:50.612 --> 00:33:52.364
where the firewall was broken.

422
00:33:55.075 --> 00:33:56.660
So it's our fault.

423
00:33:56.744 --> 00:33:59.163
- We were trying to help.
- Yes. but it went wrong.

424
00:34:01.415 --> 00:34:03.751
Where does the Iron Legion
have the hostages?

425
00:34:05.753 --> 00:34:06.754
We don't know.

426
00:34:09.465 --> 00:34:12.885
Why would they kill 50
and only kept three hostages?

427
00:34:12.968 --> 00:34:15.888
Unless you want
to go back to Costa Verde.

428
00:34:15.971 --> 00:34:17.389
This is a trap.

429
00:34:17.473 --> 00:34:18.640
We have no choice.

430
00:34:19.641 --> 00:34:22.060
Because we're not going to abandon
Angel and Zondi.

431
00:34:22.144 --> 00:34:23.145
We have to find them!

432
00:34:23.228 --> 00:34:26.273
Listen. this was a heavy blow
for the Rebellion.

433
00:34:26.356 --> 00:34:29.234
They are retreating.
They're mourning. regrouping.

434
00:34:29.318 --> 00:34:30.611
And they come here.

435
00:34:33.155 --> 00:34:34.573
When Katrina left.

436
00:34:34.656 --> 00:34:36.617
I suggested that the safest option

437
00:34:36.700 --> 00:34:38.494
was for the remaining rebels to leave the country.

438
00:34:38.577 --> 00:34:41.455
while recreating strategies.
recount the numbers.

439
00:34:43.290 --> 00:34:46.168
In the Rebellion.
there is an extremely important asset.

440
00:34:46.251 --> 00:34:47.336
with the code name Fenix.

441
00:34:47.419 --> 00:34:49.379
If anyone discovers this weapon.

442
00:34:50.756 --> 00:34:52.674
can wipe out the entire Rebellion
with one blow.

443
00:34:53.550 --> 00:34:56.053
We're going into lockdown. understand?

444
00:35:00.849 --> 00:35:02.226
- Yes.
- I'll let Thomas know.

445
00:35:10.150 --> 00:35:12.152
PRISON
GREEN COAST

446
00:35:12.236 --> 00:35:14.571
Once again. Prime Minister Díaz.

447
00:35:15.405 --> 00:35:18.450
I want to thank you
for this humble abode.

448
00:35:19.535 --> 00:35:22.621
The number of prisoners
exceeded this relic.

449
00:35:23.163 --> 00:35:26.750
So we built a state-of-the-art
in the city center.

450
00:35:28.085 --> 00:35:29.962
Consider this place a loan.

451
00:35:30.045 --> 00:35:31.839
And if you continue to impress me.

452
00:35:32.714 --> 00:35:35.926
this could become the
the Iron Legion.

453
00:35:37.052 --> 00:35:40.681
Cabrera says he emptied
a rebel terrorist cell.

454
00:35:40.764 --> 00:35:42.933
- Yes.
- That's excellent news.

455
00:35:44.017 --> 00:35:45.018
But...

456
00:35:47.771 --> 00:35:49.231
... where is Brandon Beckett?

457
00:35:50.649 --> 00:35:53.944
I'm going to find him.
But first. I have a present.

458
00:36:04.913 --> 00:36:06.290
- Olivia?
- Yes?

459
00:36:06.373 --> 00:36:08.458
Issue a press release.

460
00:36:08.542 --> 00:36:13.964
Three rebel terrorists will be executed
in my detention center in two days.

461
00:36:14.631 --> 00:36:20.304
Beckett and his friends will be forced
to Costa Verde to try and save them

462
00:36:20.387 --> 00:36:23.515
and you'll finish them off in one fell swoop.

463
00:36:25.976 --> 00:36:28.395
But... and this is important...

464
00:36:29.521 --> 00:36:32.774
... keep Brandon Beckett alive.

465
00:36:33.692 --> 00:36:35.235
I have plans for him.

466
00:36:35.319 --> 00:36:36.403
No problem.

467
00:36:37.112 --> 00:36:42.242
Until then. let's see what we can
find out about these three.

468
00:36:51.585 --> 00:36:53.587
Thabo Zondi.

469
00:36:54.963 --> 00:36:56.632
We know all about you.

470
00:36:58.842 --> 00:37:00.594
But you don't seem to have learned your lesson

471
00:37:00.677 --> 00:37:02.429
with the death of your father and grandfather in battle.

472
00:37:02.512 --> 00:37:03.889
because you signed up

473
00:37:03.972 --> 00:37:05.933
in the South African National Defense Force.

474
00:37:07.935 --> 00:37:11.229
Angel Anele.

475
00:37:12.064 --> 00:37:13.607
Former South African police officer.

476
00:37:13.690 --> 00:37:16.026
before you were caught
by Commander Modise.

477
00:37:18.320 --> 00:37:20.155
Lorenzo.

478
00:37:20.238 --> 00:37:22.532
You didn't join ERGI.

479
00:37:23.784 --> 00:37:28.080
but. somehow. you're here.
in the middle of it all.

480
00:37:28.163 --> 00:37:30.123
I have nothing against you.

481
00:37:31.416 --> 00:37:32.459
You have no digital footprint.

482
00:37:32.542 --> 00:37:35.504
You're... a mysterious man.

483
00:37:38.423 --> 00:37:39.633
ERGI.

484
00:37:41.134 --> 00:37:42.970
These bastards. aren't they?

485
00:37:43.053 --> 00:37:46.848
They'll leave evidence everywhere
for Roman's men to find.

486
00:37:50.310 --> 00:37:54.564
It seems to me that they've left everything behind.
You included. Zondi.

487
00:38:00.445 --> 00:38:03.615
I need your daughter's name
because when I'm done with you.

488
00:38:03.699 --> 00:38:06.618
she'll be the only one who can
identify your body.

489
00:38:08.078 --> 00:38:09.371
Really?

490
00:38:09.454 --> 00:38:10.831
Is it the best you've got?

491
00:38:11.540 --> 00:38:12.541
No.

492
00:38:19.840 --> 00:38:21.258
I could kill your mother.

493
00:38:23.093 --> 00:38:25.345
She's looking after your daughter. isn't she?

494
00:38:30.434 --> 00:38:32.144
Do they both have to die because of you?

495
00:38:34.646 --> 00:38:35.897
It won't break me.

496
00:38:36.982 --> 00:38:38.608
That's what everyone says.

497
00:38:40.402 --> 00:38:41.737
You're going to talk. Zondi.

498
00:38:43.780 --> 00:38:49.578
It's just a question of how much pain
you want to endure before giving in.

499
00:39:08.930 --> 00:39:11.892
So. you're Brandon Beckett.

500
00:39:12.350 --> 00:39:13.518
It would seem so.

501
00:39:14.019 --> 00:39:15.270
I've heard stories.

502
00:39:16.855 --> 00:39:18.690
I'm Zero.

503
00:39:18.774 --> 00:39:20.317
You didn't say your name.

504
00:39:21.151 --> 00:39:22.527
Skylar.

505
00:39:22.611 --> 00:39:25.697
Where can we install our technology?
We need a lot of space.

506
00:39:26.782 --> 00:39:28.784
How good is the fiber optics here?

507
00:39:30.368 --> 00:39:32.162
Is it the weapon? Is it the phoenix?

508
00:39:33.955 --> 00:39:36.166
No. It's a table.

509
00:39:39.753 --> 00:39:43.632
Are you absolutely sure
that you want help from these Americans?

510
00:39:45.342 --> 00:39:46.510
Be nice. Skylar.

511
00:39:48.011 --> 00:39:49.012
They are friends.

512
00:39:51.056 --> 00:39:52.057
New?

513
00:39:52.849 --> 00:39:53.850
Holy shit!

514
00:39:56.269 --> 00:39:57.521
You're alive.

515
00:39:59.564 --> 00:40:00.565
How?

516
00:40:02.609 --> 00:40:03.777
You're the agent.

517
00:40:04.736 --> 00:40:05.737
The Phoenix.

518
00:40:08.448 --> 00:40:10.826
You're spreading that nickname
again. aren't you?

519
00:40:12.702 --> 00:40:14.788
Spreading hope. brother.

520
00:40:14.871 --> 00:40:17.082
- We've already talked about this...
- What... I'm sorry.

521
00:40:17.165 --> 00:40:18.166
Brother?

522
00:40:18.250 --> 00:40:19.543
Yes. Skylar is my sister.

523
00:40:19.626 --> 00:40:21.837
Half of it. On our mother's side.

524
00:40:22.587 --> 00:40:25.173
I don't share genes with Roman the Repulsive.

525
00:40:26.675 --> 00:40:29.136
I'm sure that everyone
have things to catch up on.

526
00:40:30.262 --> 00:40:32.722
But in the meantime.
let's get everything ready.

527
00:40:32.806 --> 00:40:34.766
Time is running out. Yes?

528
00:40:39.104 --> 00:40:44.818
This form of torture has been described
as suffocation in slow motion.

529
00:40:44.901 --> 00:40:46.444
only with enough time

530
00:40:46.528 --> 00:40:48.905
to contemplate the inevitability
of your death.

531
00:40:54.327 --> 00:40:56.288
Your lungs will fill with water.

532
00:40:56.371 --> 00:40:58.707
The nasal cavity
and throat will close.

533
00:40:58.790 --> 00:41:00.292
You'll have trouble breathing.

534
00:41:01.418 --> 00:41:02.419
Your head will burn.

535
00:41:02.502 --> 00:41:07.090
It's physically painful
and mentally violent.

536
00:41:10.844 --> 00:41:12.888
If it goes wrong.

537
00:41:12.971 --> 00:41:14.472
is terminal hypoxia.

538
00:41:21.563 --> 00:41:22.856
If it goes well.

539
00:41:23.690 --> 00:41:25.400
is a slow and controlled death.

540
00:41:33.992 --> 00:41:35.744
It's your last chance. Zondi.

541
00:41:36.912 --> 00:41:38.455
Angel.

542
00:41:38.538 --> 00:41:39.539
Lorenzo.

543
00:41:41.458 --> 00:41:42.626
Tell me about it.

544
00:41:42.709 --> 00:41:44.920
Tell me everything Beckett told you.

545
00:41:46.463 --> 00:41:48.256
I need to know Beckett's
Beckett's strategies.

546
00:41:48.340 --> 00:41:51.301
I need to know what he does
when he comes for you.

547
00:41:57.015 --> 00:41:58.016
Well done.

548
00:42:00.560 --> 00:42:01.561
Let's get started.

549
00:42:04.814 --> 00:42:07.442
There is no longer a middle class in my country.

550
00:42:07.525 --> 00:42:11.446
The division between the rich
and the poor is catastrophic.

551
00:42:11.529 --> 00:42:13.240
This led to a revolution.

552
00:42:13.323 --> 00:42:17.327
Rotter Roman has most of
of Costa Verde in his pocket or in his hands.

553
00:42:18.703 --> 00:42:19.996
When my father was murdered.

554
00:42:20.080 --> 00:42:21.831
he was planning to open up trade with the US.

555
00:42:22.666 --> 00:42:24.376
After his death.

556
00:42:24.459 --> 00:42:27.545
Roman came to power and made sure
that the borders would be closed.

557
00:42:28.213 --> 00:42:32.676
Saying that the country
had to be self-sufficient.

558
00:42:32.759 --> 00:42:37.681
But the nation has become impoverished and the
infrastructure is crumbling.

559
00:42:38.348 --> 00:42:39.933
Roman doesn't want to open the borders.

560
00:42:41.017 --> 00:42:42.644
because you want to expand them

561
00:42:43.895 --> 00:42:46.982
to other countries. such as Tierra Nueva.

562
00:42:49.150 --> 00:42:51.027
But for that. he needs a war.

563
00:42:51.611 --> 00:42:52.612
Exactly.

564
00:42:54.906 --> 00:42:56.032
We're up and running.

565
00:42:57.867 --> 00:42:59.035
After my injuries.

566
00:43:00.036 --> 00:43:03.290
I couldn't get back to the battlefield.

567
00:43:03.373 --> 00:43:05.750
but I'm trying to do
my best remotely.

568
00:43:06.418 --> 00:43:10.880
Skylar and I have overcome
Roman's media blackout.

569
00:43:10.964 --> 00:43:14.801
spreading the truth.
but I hope someone is listening.

570
00:43:15.593 --> 00:43:16.636
But they have to be quick.

571
00:43:16.720 --> 00:43:18.305
Even with a signal deviation.

572
00:43:18.388 --> 00:43:20.890
can end up tracing
the rupture back to you.

573
00:43:24.144 --> 00:43:25.603
We learned that the hard way.

574
00:43:26.563 --> 00:43:27.689
What can we do. Nova?

575
00:43:35.238 --> 00:43:36.323
What a load of crap.

576
00:43:39.909 --> 00:43:42.662
This has just arrived. Hold on.

577
00:43:45.040 --> 00:43:46.291
Let me translate.

578
00:43:47.000 --> 00:43:48.376
THREE TERRORISTS WILL BE EXECUTED!

579
00:43:48.460 --> 00:43:51.171
Angel. Zondi and Lorenzo
will be executed.

580
00:43:53.256 --> 00:43:54.257
Executed?

581
00:43:57.177 --> 00:43:58.845
Roman wants to make an example of them.

582
00:44:00.138 --> 00:44:01.598
If you consider him a "terrorist"

583
00:44:01.681 --> 00:44:04.934
and caught in Costa Verde.
he will be sentenced to death.

584
00:44:06.478 --> 00:44:09.397
"The execution is tomorrow
at the downtown detention center."

585
00:44:10.648 --> 00:44:11.691
How do we stop it?

586
00:44:13.943 --> 00:44:14.944
We can't.

587
00:44:16.363 --> 00:44:20.325
We have few resources.
We lost so many in the last attack.

588
00:44:21.076 --> 00:44:24.204
Roman's detention center
is in the middle of the city

589
00:44:24.287 --> 00:44:26.164
and is impenetrable.

590
00:44:27.165 --> 00:44:31.127
We don't have time to go in

591
00:44:31.211 --> 00:44:32.837
without most of our people dying.

592
00:44:32.921 --> 00:44:34.172
But we have a lot of rebels here.

593
00:44:34.255 --> 00:44:36.299
Surely there are enough of us to attack.

594
00:44:36.383 --> 00:44:38.760
We can't afford
of losing anyone else.

595
00:44:38.843 --> 00:44:41.596
Otherwise.
there will be no one to defend the cause.

596
00:44:45.975 --> 00:44:48.269
We're talking about Angel and Zondi. Nova!

597
00:44:51.940 --> 00:44:56.194
The Phoenix Rebellion
is fighting for the soul of my country.

598
00:45:01.157 --> 00:45:04.744
The cause is much bigger
than a few individuals.

599
00:45:06.746 --> 00:45:10.625
Angel. Zondi and Lorenzo
knew this when they enlisted.

600
00:45:13.044 --> 00:45:16.881
I'm sorry. but a rescue mission
is too risky for the movement.

601
00:45:18.466 --> 00:45:20.760
Okay. we understand. Nova. We understand. Nova.

602
00:45:20.844 --> 00:45:22.262
and we respect your choice.

603
00:45:24.514 --> 00:45:27.600
But let's move forward.
Let's bring our friends.

604
00:45:31.146 --> 00:45:32.230
So. good luck.

605
00:45:37.068 --> 00:45:38.236
New.

606
00:45:40.196 --> 00:45:41.739
It's really good to see you again.

607
00:45:45.869 --> 00:45:47.996
Thank you for letting us come here.

608
00:45:50.039 --> 00:45:51.040
But please.

609
00:45:52.750 --> 00:45:57.922
don't compromise the plans for my country
to appease your egos.

610
00:46:10.685 --> 00:46:12.604
There has to be a way in. right?

611
00:46:16.274 --> 00:46:17.275
I don't know.

612
00:46:47.805 --> 00:46:51.351
All this pain was caused
by Brandon Beckett.

613
00:46:53.394 --> 00:46:55.104
But you know that. don't you?

614
00:46:56.689 --> 00:46:59.817
He brought the Iron Legion to you.

615
00:47:05.281 --> 00:47:09.118
Americans like Brandon Beckett
believe they have freedom.

616
00:47:09.202 --> 00:47:11.329
but America is a country
where money rules.

617
00:47:13.581 --> 00:47:18.211
I'm making Costa Verde
equal for everyone.

618
00:47:19.712 --> 00:47:22.715
But the US feels threatened
by this new way of life.

619
00:47:26.010 --> 00:47:30.515
Once. my brother tried to open
our doors to the rest of the world.

620
00:47:31.724 --> 00:47:33.351
and we can see what happened.

621
00:47:34.060 --> 00:47:35.812
People don't want this.

622
00:47:36.980 --> 00:47:40.858
They want protection. security.

623
00:47:41.526 --> 00:47:44.070
And that's what I'm giving.

624
00:47:45.280 --> 00:47:48.616
I'm taking Costa Verde into the future.

625
00:47:48.700 --> 00:47:53.830
to a new era in which the United States
no longer influences the rest of the world.

626
00:47:54.998 --> 00:47:58.710
Soon. other countries will look to
Costa Verde as the best way to live.

627
00:48:01.671 --> 00:48:05.675
And I want you to be part of it. son.

628
00:48:09.762 --> 00:48:14.851
But loyalty to Brandon Beckett

629
00:48:14.934 --> 00:48:17.186
has consequences.

630
00:49:10.323 --> 00:49:11.366
What do you want. son?

631
00:49:18.665 --> 00:49:20.291
I see potential in you.

632
00:49:29.926 --> 00:49:32.679
Wasted by Brandon Beckett
when he abandoned you.

633
00:49:46.693 --> 00:49:48.444
You can be a leader. Zondi.

634
00:50:08.464 --> 00:50:10.466
Lead for me

635
00:50:10.550 --> 00:50:12.927
and I will make your legacy immortal.

636
00:50:32.697 --> 00:50:36.951
Whatever happens after this.
for the rest of your life.

637
00:50:37.994 --> 00:50:42.915
everything from that moment on...

638
00:50:44.917 --> 00:50:46.335
... it's a gift from me.

639
00:50:52.258 --> 00:50:53.760
I give you life.

640
00:51:02.310 --> 00:51:03.978
It's morphine.

641
00:51:04.061 --> 00:51:06.147
I'm here to help you. son.

642
00:51:47.021 --> 00:51:49.190
Keep going. I thought
everyone was already asleep.

643
00:51:49.273 --> 00:51:51.734
That's all right.
It was over anyway.

644
00:51:53.486 --> 00:51:55.905
Yeah. I can't believe you're alive. Nova.

645
00:51:55.988 --> 00:51:58.366
I'm very grateful. man. We didn't know.

646
00:52:01.035 --> 00:52:06.249
For 24 hours. I had several
cardiac arrests. I'm lucky to be here.

647
00:52:08.000 --> 00:52:11.170
Oh. shit! Look at yourself.

648
00:52:11.796 --> 00:52:14.590
Shot four times. reborn
from the ashes. That's why they call you Phoenix.

649
00:52:15.424 --> 00:52:16.425
I just came to get some aspirin.

650
00:52:16.509 --> 00:52:18.886
Looking at those screens
is giving me a headache.

651
00:52:20.137 --> 00:52:23.724
I applaud your resilience in finding
a way into the detention center.

652
00:52:25.476 --> 00:52:27.645
Brandon and I can't give up.

653
00:52:27.728 --> 00:52:29.480
We lost our ERGI team.

654
00:52:31.524 --> 00:52:32.984
We lost so many others.

655
00:52:35.069 --> 00:52:36.821
I don't want to lose anyone else.

656
00:52:38.072 --> 00:52:40.741
That's funny about the ERGI team.

657
00:52:43.035 --> 00:52:45.037
All this time we've spent together.

658
00:52:45.121 --> 00:52:50.084
neither you nor Brandon mentioned

659
00:52:50.167 --> 00:52:53.588
that Yuki Mifune
was part of your team.

660
00:52:54.839 --> 00:52:58.301
Lady Death.
The assassin who killed my father.

661
00:53:02.513 --> 00:53:03.514
Good.

662
00:53:05.725 --> 00:53:06.851
no one is perfect.

663
00:53:09.353 --> 00:53:11.564
Look. Nova. we're all soldiers here.

664
00:53:11.647 --> 00:53:13.399
We all killed those we were told to kill.

665
00:53:13.482 --> 00:53:15.276
I assure you. it's not personal.

666
00:53:17.153 --> 00:53:18.154
Right. guys?

667
00:53:18.237 --> 00:53:22.158
It was personal for me. for my family
and for the people of Costa Verde.

668
00:53:22.241 --> 00:53:26.203
If she hadn't fired.
none of this would be happening!

669
00:53:26.287 --> 00:53:27.288
Yes.

670
00:53:28.998 --> 00:53:30.291
- She saved my life.
- Come on!

671
00:53:30.374 --> 00:53:33.294
She saved Brandon's life.
She saved so many lives. Nova.

672
00:53:39.842 --> 00:53:40.927
Zero...

673
00:53:44.096 --> 00:53:47.600
... in all the missions you entered.

674
00:53:47.683 --> 00:53:51.228
you saved the day and walked away.

675
00:53:53.773 --> 00:53:58.736
But have you ever wondered
what happens next?

676
00:54:00.154 --> 00:54:04.408
Because everything you do
has a domino effect.

677
00:54:04.492 --> 00:54:08.955
This Lady Death on your team. Yuki.

678
00:54:10.331 --> 00:54:15.711
it all started
when he killed my father for money.

679
00:54:17.129 --> 00:54:22.343
And you receive it without consequences.

680
00:54:22.426 --> 00:54:24.053
Have you ever thought about it?

681
00:54:34.981 --> 00:54:40.027
I've already died once because of it.

682
00:54:42.279 --> 00:54:43.698
And that changed me.

683
00:54:47.368 --> 00:54:52.957
I appreciate everything you and Brandon
have done for the Rebellion.

684
00:54:53.040 --> 00:54:59.547
But I don't think bringing in
foreign agents was the best idea.

685
00:54:59.630 --> 00:55:00.840
No. wait. Listen to me.

686
00:55:01.674 --> 00:55:05.177
If we kill Roman Díaz.
all these problems will disappear.

687
00:55:05.261 --> 00:55:08.264
They won't disappear! No!

688
00:55:08.347 --> 00:55:11.475
Eliminating a leader doesn't solve problems.

689
00:55:11.559 --> 00:55:15.438
It just creates a power vacuum
for the next tyrant to occupy!

690
00:55:17.606 --> 00:55:22.236
It's not the man who needs to be
replaced. it's the system that needs to change!

691
00:55:27.950 --> 00:55:32.329
To be honest.
I really don't know how to do that.

692
00:55:38.586 --> 00:55:39.670
Good evening. Zero.

693
00:56:06.614 --> 00:56:07.615
Zondi?

694
00:56:13.704 --> 00:56:14.705
Zondi!

695
00:56:17.917 --> 00:56:19.585
I'm here with you.

696
00:56:20.961 --> 00:56:23.297
We'll get out of here. I promise.

697
00:56:26.759 --> 00:56:28.302
How?

698
00:56:30.763 --> 00:56:32.098
No one is coming to save us.

699
00:56:32.181 --> 00:56:34.266
No. That's not true.

700
00:56:34.350 --> 00:56:36.185
The Rebellion would never leave us.

701
00:56:37.728 --> 00:56:42.399
Beckett led the Legion to us.
he wanted us dead.

702
00:56:44.693 --> 00:56:49.198
Beckett and Zero saved us
in Kovalov's compound.

703
00:56:50.241 --> 00:56:52.284
They risked their lives
so that we could escape.

704
00:56:52.368 --> 00:56:53.536
Have you forgotten that?

705
00:56:53.619 --> 00:56:54.995
Then they turned their backs on us.

706
00:56:57.581 --> 00:56:58.874
They left us. Angel.

707
00:57:01.335 --> 00:57:05.506
When there was an opportunity
for them to come back and help us.

708
00:57:06.590 --> 00:57:08.008
they abandoned us again.

709
00:57:09.635 --> 00:57:11.137
What got us here.

710
00:57:16.058 --> 00:57:19.478
Beckett is not a leader.
he's just a soldier.

711
00:57:19.562 --> 00:57:20.688
Even without a country.

712
00:57:20.771 --> 00:57:23.315
listens to an authority that is not himself.

713
00:57:25.109 --> 00:57:26.110
He's weak.

714
00:57:27.695 --> 00:57:29.363
This has never been our battle.

715
00:57:30.823 --> 00:57:35.077
We had a mission.
You chose to stay and so did I.

716
00:57:35.161 --> 00:57:36.579
But. brother. I promise...

717
00:57:36.662 --> 00:57:38.664
I don't need your compassion.

718
00:57:43.586 --> 00:57:47.756
Help will come. You'll see.

719
00:57:57.141 --> 00:57:59.977
These plans and diagrams
are the best I could find.

720
00:58:00.060 --> 00:58:02.354
They detail the detention center
on all levels.

721
00:58:02.438 --> 00:58:04.815
but. honestly.
I don't see a weak point.

722
00:58:04.899 --> 00:58:07.318
But you're the marine. not me.

723
00:58:09.778 --> 00:58:11.947
Thanks. Pete. They're great.

724
00:58:12.865 --> 00:58:13.949
What else can I do?

725
00:58:14.033 --> 00:58:17.369
There must be something.
Those people were killed when I...

726
00:58:17.453 --> 00:58:20.289
It's not your fault. okay?

727
00:58:21.832 --> 00:58:22.875
We didn't know that the Legion

728
00:58:22.958 --> 00:58:25.127
would trace our call
to the Rebellion.

729
00:58:27.463 --> 00:58:29.715
The Legion took their lives.

730
00:58:29.798 --> 00:58:32.801
Those deaths are their fault. not yours.

731
00:58:32.885 --> 00:58:35.221
Whoever traced that signal
was a professional. Brandon.

732
00:58:35.304 --> 00:58:36.764
A programming savant.

733
00:58:36.847 --> 00:58:39.141
I've never seen anything like it.

734
00:58:39.225 --> 00:58:41.060
Be careful. Are you all right?

735
00:58:42.394 --> 00:58:45.022
And we will. Thanks for the plants.

736
00:58:45.105 --> 00:58:46.106
Sorry. man.

737
00:58:46.190 --> 00:58:47.191
Well done. Pete.

738
00:58:51.737 --> 00:58:54.490
I had an intense conversation with Nova.

739
00:58:54.573 --> 00:58:55.950
The guy has changed.

740
00:58:58.369 --> 00:59:00.454
Well. four bullets will do that.

741
00:59:02.748 --> 00:59:06.001
He wanted to know why his father
was killed by an ERGI member.

742
00:59:08.003 --> 00:59:09.004
He's right.

743
00:59:11.131 --> 00:59:12.299
You do this job

744
00:59:12.383 --> 00:59:14.885
and you always believe that you're
on the right side of the fight...

745
00:59:15.928 --> 00:59:18.305
But you're always
on the wrong side of someone else.

746
00:59:19.139 --> 00:59:20.808
That's very eloquent.

747
00:59:20.891 --> 00:59:23.435
Why weren't you there
when I spoke to Nova?

748
00:59:25.729 --> 00:59:27.898
Because it was here.

749
00:59:28.899 --> 00:59:31.860
Trying to find a way
to get into this damned fortress.

750
00:59:34.488 --> 00:59:36.031
I can't see a way in.

751
00:59:37.199 --> 00:59:39.368
The sewer tunnels don't work.

752
00:59:39.451 --> 00:59:41.161
It's too risky to come out on top.

753
00:59:41.245 --> 00:59:44.456
It's heavily armored and guarded all around.

754
00:59:48.711 --> 00:59:49.712
Nova may be right.

755
00:59:50.587 --> 00:59:52.464
We don't have time
to find an entrance.

756
00:59:52.548 --> 00:59:54.091
But we can't give up. B.

757
00:59:54.174 --> 00:59:55.509
They're not going to die like that.

758
00:59:57.261 --> 00:59:59.471
We still have a few hours.

759
00:59:59.555 --> 01:00:00.556
Okay.

760
01:00:02.516 --> 01:00:03.642
Let's try again.

761
01:00:05.853 --> 01:00:07.688
These are the plants that PI sent you.

762
01:00:10.566 --> 01:00:13.944
And if we take one of the old vans.

763
01:00:14.028 --> 01:00:16.697
fixing
and break down the front gate?

764
01:00:18.115 --> 01:00:19.700
That's what they expect us to do.

765
01:00:20.784 --> 01:00:23.162
We'll load up with weapons in hand.

766
01:00:24.038 --> 01:00:25.914
But we can't do that.
just the two of us.

767
01:00:26.415 --> 01:00:27.791
- Well?
- Anything?

768
01:00:28.500 --> 01:00:29.501
No.

769
01:00:33.964 --> 01:00:37.343
Did Thomas ever tell you
about the mission in Costa Verde?

770
01:00:38.510 --> 01:00:40.346
I've just been reminded of her.

771
01:00:41.764 --> 01:00:45.309
We were in a similar situation.
We just couldn't find a way in.

772
01:00:49.021 --> 01:00:50.022
So what did they do?

773
01:00:51.607 --> 01:00:52.691
Your father said:

774
01:00:52.775 --> 01:00:56.487
"If you can't see an entrance.
find out what theirs is."

775
01:01:02.409 --> 01:01:03.535
That's the answer.

776
01:01:06.163 --> 01:01:07.164
Wait. what?

777
01:01:11.293 --> 01:01:13.170
We didn't attack the detention center.

778
01:01:14.046 --> 01:01:16.924
We attacked the convoy
taking the hostages there.

779
01:01:17.007 --> 01:01:20.344
We ambushed them before they reached the prison.

780
01:01:21.470 --> 01:01:24.723
They'll have protection.
But we'll have the element of surprise.

781
01:01:27.434 --> 01:01:28.435
That could work.

782
01:01:30.270 --> 01:01:32.648
We know they're going to the detention center

783
01:01:32.731 --> 01:01:34.441
in the middle of the city.

784
01:01:34.525 --> 01:01:38.070
but we don't know which direction they're coming from.

785
01:01:38.153 --> 01:01:39.947
It doesn't matter where they come from.

786
01:01:40.030 --> 01:01:42.533
as long as we can bring the escort
here.

787
01:01:44.535 --> 01:01:46.036
We've created a death box.

788
01:01:50.874 --> 01:01:53.419
My brother and I
can take you there.

789
01:01:53.502 --> 01:01:55.379
We're going to hack into their GPS system.

790
01:01:55.462 --> 01:01:57.548
- Can you do that?
- Yes.

791
01:01:57.631 --> 01:02:00.008
Their eyes are closed.

792
01:02:00.092 --> 01:02:03.345
We can help. Nova. From here.

793
01:02:11.061 --> 01:02:12.354
Okay.

794
01:02:13.313 --> 01:02:17.693
But just you and me. And only from here. Is that all right?

795
01:02:18.402 --> 01:02:19.736
Thank you.

796
01:02:22.364 --> 01:02:25.576
Do you really think you can face
the Iron Legion alone?

797
01:02:29.455 --> 01:02:31.415
We've had worse odds.

798
01:02:31.498 --> 01:02:33.292
And this time we have reinforcements.

799
01:02:39.173 --> 01:02:40.632
Are these your reinforcements?

800
01:02:41.425 --> 01:02:44.928
Congratulations. you've doubled
your size to four.

801
01:02:45.012 --> 01:02:47.389
Don't look at me. kid.
I'm just the getaway driver.

802
01:02:49.683 --> 01:02:50.976
So there are only three.

803
01:02:52.060 --> 01:02:54.730
Three arrive. One shot. one death.

804
01:02:55.772 --> 01:02:56.773
One shot. one death.

805
01:02:59.860 --> 01:03:04.239
In the death box.
Brandon and Thomas will be on sentry duty.

806
01:03:05.782 --> 01:03:08.243
We need you on the same team.

807
01:03:08.327 --> 01:03:10.078
Hello. old friend.

808
01:03:14.875 --> 01:03:17.669
I'll be in charge of evacuating the hostages.

809
01:03:17.753 --> 01:03:19.087
Even with armor-piercing bullets.

810
01:03:19.171 --> 01:03:22.758
can a .50 caliber penetrate
in an armored vehicle like that?

811
01:03:22.841 --> 01:03:25.093
Yes. especially.
if you know where to hit.

812
01:03:25.928 --> 01:03:27.012
You're looking for the joints.

813
01:03:30.516 --> 01:03:33.519
Nova and Skylar.
you are our eyes and ears.

814
01:03:33.602 --> 01:03:36.605
Make sure
Cinderella arrives at the ball.

815
01:03:38.607 --> 01:03:43.070
GPS locator. don't lose it.
Or we'll lose you.

816
01:03:45.197 --> 01:03:48.659
And. Frost. you take care of the extraction.
Let's get inside quickly.

817
01:03:48.742 --> 01:03:50.118
Maybe it's time to improve.

818
01:03:52.287 --> 01:03:54.498
You'll break your back carrying it.

819
01:04:00.712 --> 01:04:03.173
They should leave first thing in the morning.

820
01:04:03.257 --> 01:04:06.301
We have to be ready. Let's load up.

821
01:04:13.016 --> 01:04:16.478
I'm glad you're here. Both of you.

822
01:04:17.771 --> 01:04:23.569
Thank you for coming.
This is my dream team.

823
01:04:26.154 --> 01:04:28.490
Side by side until the end. B.
There's no other way.

824
01:04:55.309 --> 01:04:57.311
I'm sorry you were
dragged into this.

825
01:05:00.147 --> 01:05:01.356
Dragged?

826
01:05:02.107 --> 01:05:07.696
No. I came of my own free will.
You're my son. for God's sake.

827
01:05:13.243 --> 01:05:16.705
It's hard to believe that one country
can cause us so much turmoil.

828
01:05:18.332 --> 01:05:21.043
I think that's the curse of Costa Verde.

829
01:05:25.005 --> 01:05:27.466
Throughout my time in the Navy.

830
01:05:27.549 --> 01:05:29.968
I only did one posting here.

831
01:05:31.678 --> 01:05:36.850
But I remember a sergeant
we had before the mission.

832
01:05:39.186 --> 01:05:42.898
that made us write
our own obituaries.

833
01:05:44.775 --> 01:05:47.361
Yes. he was such a geek.

834
01:05:50.364 --> 01:05:52.699
I think he realized that.

835
01:05:56.203 --> 01:06:00.540
if we did that. we'd fight harder
and we wouldn't be afraid of death.

836
01:06:03.794 --> 01:06:05.629
Death? Shit!

837
01:06:08.465 --> 01:06:10.092
I spit on death.

838
01:06:17.224 --> 01:06:19.059
But you know what I was afraid of?

839
01:06:23.939 --> 01:06:28.735
I was afraid I'd never see you again.

840
01:06:32.698 --> 01:06:33.949
I've never...

841
01:06:35.617 --> 01:06:37.452
I was never there enough.

842
01:06:38.412 --> 01:06:40.205
I wasn't there.

843
01:06:45.252 --> 01:06:52.259
All that lost time...
That... lost time.

844
01:06:52.426 --> 01:06:54.344
Sorry.

845
01:06:58.682 --> 01:07:03.395
Of everything I've been through in my career.
everything I've done.

846
01:07:04.688 --> 01:07:06.606
did anything really matter?

847
01:07:09.985 --> 01:07:13.405
Have I ever done anything
to change things?

848
01:07:14.489 --> 01:07:16.074
I don't know.

849
01:07:21.329 --> 01:07:22.706
I don't know... what...

850
01:07:25.625 --> 01:07:28.086
Look. Yes. it's changed.

851
01:07:29.629 --> 01:07:33.508
You made a difference.
You made the difference for me.

852
01:07:51.359 --> 01:07:54.738
I still don't understand
why you won't go back with him.

853
01:08:00.786 --> 01:08:01.828
Mr. Rosenberg?

854
01:08:02.913 --> 01:08:05.791
Katrina. you can call me Zero.

855
01:08:05.874 --> 01:08:08.335
- Mr. Zero.
- Yes. Mr. Zero.

856
01:08:08.418 --> 01:08:12.380
Let me go with you.
Zondi saved my life. I owe him.

857
01:08:12.464 --> 01:08:14.466
Your orders were to stay.

858
01:08:14.549 --> 01:08:16.343
And it's not my place to argue.

859
01:08:16.426 --> 01:08:18.261
But there has to be something I can do.

860
01:08:18.345 --> 01:08:21.181
There. You stay here.
help these people get ready.

861
01:08:22.098 --> 01:08:26.478
Your time to fight will come. Katrina.
Today is not that day. Are you all right?

862
01:08:32.025 --> 01:08:34.820
May fate be in your favor.

863
01:08:35.487 --> 01:08:36.696
Thank you.

864
01:08:43.578 --> 01:08:46.623
Is it just me
or does everyone here make you feel old?

865
01:08:46.706 --> 01:08:50.418
We're not old. we're experienced.

866
01:08:52.420 --> 01:08:55.298
They're too young
to go into battle. B.

867
01:08:57.259 --> 01:09:00.345
Look at Zondi. He was so young
and refreshed when we met him.

868
01:09:02.764 --> 01:09:04.057
Look how I left him.

869
01:09:05.517 --> 01:09:07.602
I can't forget Angel's words.

870
01:09:09.312 --> 01:09:10.772
I should have stayed longer.

871
01:09:10.856 --> 01:09:12.148
It wasn't our orders. B.

872
01:09:12.941 --> 01:09:15.277
Zondi chose to stay.
You told him it was dangerous.

873
01:09:15.360 --> 01:09:16.528
He's just a kid. man.

874
01:09:17.404 --> 01:09:19.030
With Modise dead...

875
01:09:21.491 --> 01:09:22.576
Now I understand.

876
01:09:23.410 --> 01:09:25.036
We finish a mission and go home.

877
01:09:25.120 --> 01:09:28.331
but it's not just about the state
we leave the country.

878
01:09:29.583 --> 01:09:31.793
is about the state
we leave people in.

879
01:09:31.877 --> 01:09:33.420
Yes.

880
01:09:33.503 --> 01:09:35.589
But now is not the time
to doubt our training

881
01:09:35.672 --> 01:09:37.424
or what we've been doing for years. B.

882
01:09:38.758 --> 01:09:40.176
Because we have a job to do.

883
01:09:42.429 --> 01:09:43.430
Are you all right?

884
01:10:14.794 --> 01:10:16.046
Seat belts!

885
01:10:17.422 --> 01:10:19.841
I don't want them to get hurt before the execution.

886
01:10:52.791 --> 01:10:55.585
Four-vehicle escort.
just as we thought. Route 12.

887
01:10:55.669 --> 01:10:57.379
Let's get into their GPS.

888
01:11:16.898 --> 01:11:18.358
There you are.

889
01:11:20.777 --> 01:11:22.112
We need the license plates.

890
01:11:29.411 --> 01:11:31.538
I may need the make
and model of the car.

891
01:11:35.125 --> 01:11:38.086
Then we searched for the car's
the car's GPS satellite system.

892
01:11:41.089 --> 01:11:44.551
Let me mark the area
where the vehicles travel and...

893
01:11:46.261 --> 01:11:47.554
Bam.

894
01:12:14.998 --> 01:12:16.875
This way. you idiot.

895
01:12:25.925 --> 01:12:30.597
No. don't question it. Just do what you're told.

896
01:12:32.223 --> 01:12:33.850
Because I need you to go...

897
01:12:36.561 --> 01:12:37.562
to the right.

898
01:12:37.645 --> 01:12:38.980
Turn right onto Calle Ocho

899
01:12:39.064 --> 01:12:40.315
Turn right.

900
01:12:52.160 --> 01:12:53.787
Turn left.

901
01:13:11.554 --> 01:13:13.932
Escort close to you.
Two minutes. Get ready.

902
01:13:27.654 --> 01:13:28.696
Thirty seconds.

903
01:13:30.490 --> 01:13:35.161
Sentry One in position.
As planned. I attack the vehicle in front.

904
01:13:36.162 --> 01:13:38.540
Sentry Two.
You get the armored truck.

905
01:13:39.958 --> 01:13:42.043
Sentry Two in position.

906
01:13:42.127 --> 01:13:44.462
Zero. you have the last vehicle.

907
01:13:44.546 --> 01:13:46.756
In position. Here we go.

908
01:13:55.223 --> 01:13:56.474
The escort has arrived.

909
01:13:57.600 --> 01:13:59.269
Sentinel One decides.

910
01:14:06.818 --> 01:14:07.902
Sentinel One here.

911
01:14:08.987 --> 01:14:12.031
Sentinel Two. on my count.

912
01:14:15.410 --> 01:14:16.578
Something's not right.

913
01:14:16.661 --> 01:14:21.457
Green light in three... two... one. Fire!

914
01:14:26.880 --> 01:14:28.047
Shoot the tire or something.

915
01:14:29.883 --> 01:14:31.092
- Shit!
- What the...

916
01:14:36.014 --> 01:14:37.015
Mer...

917
01:14:45.732 --> 01:14:47.317
Contact made!

918
01:14:48.568 --> 01:14:50.778
Everybody out! Cover fire!

919
01:14:53.865 --> 01:14:56.159
Get out! Everybody out!

920
01:15:18.723 --> 01:15:20.850
Up here. you idiot! Look up here.

921
01:15:22.143 --> 01:15:24.604
Shooter! Get down!

922
01:15:51.965 --> 01:15:55.093
Beckett! Where are you?

923
01:16:04.060 --> 01:16:06.104
You're late. Kruger! What the hell is going on?

924
01:16:06.187 --> 01:16:09.023
The Americans have cornered us!
Send reinforcements now!

925
01:16:09.107 --> 01:16:12.610
Get on with it! You're the Iron Legion!
We pay you for that!

926
01:16:12.694 --> 01:16:16.489
If I don't send reinforcements now.
this mess will spread even further.

927
01:16:16.572 --> 01:16:18.324
I don't even know where it is!

928
01:16:18.408 --> 01:16:20.493
Follow the sound of the war zone in your street!

929
01:16:20.576 --> 01:16:21.828
Fucking asshole!

930
01:16:34.716 --> 01:16:35.717
Watch my back!

931
01:16:46.436 --> 01:16:48.771
Yayan! Cover fire!

932
01:16:48.855 --> 01:16:50.815
Everybody out. now!

933
01:16:51.566 --> 01:16:52.900
Yayan. come with me!

934
01:17:02.910 --> 01:17:08.166
Vince. move! Now!

935
01:17:08.249 --> 01:17:09.625
Come on.

936
01:17:15.006 --> 01:17:16.090
Son of a...

937
01:18:07.850 --> 01:18:08.851
Let's go!

938
01:18:21.906 --> 01:18:23.533
They're using the hostages as shields!

939
01:18:50.351 --> 01:18:55.773
When you get to hell.
tell them Angel sent you.

940
01:19:05.366 --> 01:19:06.492
Shit!

941
01:19:18.713 --> 01:19:20.339
I'm trapped.

942
01:19:20.423 --> 01:19:21.424
I'll take care of it.

943
01:19:26.971 --> 01:19:28.473
Fuck!

944
01:19:33.895 --> 01:19:35.354
Let's go!

945
01:19:40.109 --> 01:19:41.110
Fuck!

946
01:19:51.162 --> 01:19:54.332
Zondi has just evacuated.
He has no idea where to find us.

947
01:19:55.208 --> 01:19:58.169
Skylar. see if you can locate Zondi
on the surveillance cameras.

948
01:19:58.252 --> 01:19:59.337
Understood. Right away.

949
01:20:00.546 --> 01:20:02.757
Find Angel.
She's still somewhere in the middle.

950
01:20:10.723 --> 01:20:12.308
I don't see anyone here.

951
01:20:14.644 --> 01:20:17.396
Sentinel One. leaving his position.

952
01:20:17.480 --> 01:20:19.732
Understood. I'm going after Lorenzo.

953
01:20:50.763 --> 01:20:51.764
Fuck!

954
01:21:11.492 --> 01:21:13.703
Damn! I don't have a clear shot.

955
01:21:23.212 --> 01:21:25.506
I'll take care of it. Evacuate.

956
01:21:25.590 --> 01:21:28.175
Understood. I'll meet Frost.

957
01:21:37.310 --> 01:21:38.728
It's not a fucking game.

958
01:21:52.158 --> 01:21:56.329
Fuck it. I'm going to kill you now.

959
01:22:16.974 --> 01:22:18.768
Ezekiel Rosenberg.

960
01:22:19.685 --> 01:22:20.936
I've heard of you.

961
01:22:22.563 --> 01:22:24.732
You're Beckett's boss. right?

962
01:22:28.277 --> 01:22:29.737
My name is Zero. asshole.

963
01:24:58.469 --> 01:24:59.720
Kruger is dead.

964
01:25:01.222 --> 01:25:02.890
I have Angel and Lorenzo with me.

965
01:25:03.682 --> 01:25:05.017
Free and safe.

966
01:25:05.100 --> 01:25:08.687
You have to get out of there.
Get the helicopter ready to take off.

967
01:25:08.771 --> 01:25:10.481
We have to hurry. Let's go!

968
01:25:11.857 --> 01:25:13.442
The police are raiding the area.

969
01:25:14.610 --> 01:25:15.611
Hello?

970
01:25:16.695 --> 01:25:19.073
Nova. can you see a way out of here?

971
01:25:21.242 --> 01:25:22.326
New?

972
01:25:23.994 --> 01:25:24.995
Zero. answer.

973
01:25:31.877 --> 01:25:35.714
Beckett. Zero. do you read?
Wait. the radios aren't working.

974
01:25:35.798 --> 01:25:37.842
- Turn them back on.
- What do you think I'm trying to do?

975
01:25:46.267 --> 01:25:47.518
Brandon. come in.

976
01:25:49.228 --> 01:25:53.148
I bumped into your friend Zondi
on the way to the meeting point.

977
01:25:53.232 --> 01:25:55.317
It seems that luck
may be on our side today.

978
01:25:59.572 --> 01:26:00.573
Frost!

979
01:26:01.365 --> 01:26:02.408
It's about time.

980
01:26:04.660 --> 01:26:06.078
Where are Zondi and Beckett?

981
01:26:07.705 --> 01:26:08.956
Wait. they should be here.

982
01:26:10.666 --> 01:26:14.753
Nova. Skylar. have any of you
located the Beckett's GPS?

983
01:26:18.632 --> 01:26:20.801
Nova. Skylar. are you listening?

984
01:26:24.471 --> 01:26:27.516
Shit! Communications are down.

985
01:26:30.311 --> 01:26:32.354
Zondi. are we all right?

986
01:26:32.938 --> 01:26:34.356
Everything's fine.

987
01:26:34.440 --> 01:26:35.816
Get off at the ramp to San Marino

988
01:26:35.900 --> 01:26:38.152
Our evacuation is on the south side of the city.

989
01:26:38.235 --> 01:26:40.070
Go that way. we'll guide you.

990
01:26:45.910 --> 01:26:47.912
I can't find what's
blocking our signal.

991
01:26:49.038 --> 01:26:51.373
They still have the locators.
I'm just trying to see them.

992
01:26:54.168 --> 01:26:55.753
Who the hell was that?

993
01:26:55.836 --> 01:26:57.171
- Where's our sign?
- No.

994
01:26:58.172 --> 01:27:01.133
No. They're trying to
into our system. Nova.

995
01:27:04.553 --> 01:27:05.679
What the hell?

996
01:27:31.705 --> 01:27:32.831
Zondi. what are you doing?

997
01:27:34.166 --> 01:27:35.668
What the hell is going on?

998
01:27:36.293 --> 01:27:40.047
You made your choices. Brandon Beckett.
I made mine.

999
01:27:40.130 --> 01:27:41.507
I risked everything for you!

1000
01:27:41.590 --> 01:27:42.841
You're too late.

1001
01:27:43.926 --> 01:27:45.010
Shit!

1002
01:27:45.094 --> 01:27:46.303
Oh my God!

1003
01:27:54.186 --> 01:27:56.689
Fuck! It's that fucking cabron. Díaz.

1004
01:27:57.272 --> 01:27:59.358
Damn it! I've only got one shot left.

1005
01:27:59.441 --> 01:28:01.151
How long for a direct call?

1006
01:28:01.235 --> 01:28:03.112
We can reverse and get out of here.

1007
01:28:03.195 --> 01:28:04.697
We're not going to win this one. son.

1008
01:28:05.239 --> 01:28:07.491
Give it here!

1009
01:28:08.742 --> 01:28:12.788
Whatever happens.
stay strong. Did you hear that?

1010
01:28:13.580 --> 01:28:16.208
I should have seen this coming. I'm sorry. Dad.

1011
01:28:16.291 --> 01:28:17.668
Go. Brandon.

1012
01:28:19.420 --> 01:28:20.421
Go!

1013
01:28:21.296 --> 01:28:23.090
- We're in this together.
- Yes.

1014
01:28:45.320 --> 01:28:46.405
Brandon.

1015
01:28:49.158 --> 01:28:51.160
I just want you to know one thing.

1016
01:28:51.243 --> 01:28:53.704
You're the best thing that ever happened to me.

1017
01:28:55.873 --> 01:28:59.418
Stay discreet and alert.
and don't forget.

1018
01:29:01.920 --> 01:29:03.047
semper fi. kid.

1019
01:29:17.186 --> 01:29:18.187
Don't shoot!

1020
01:29:38.957 --> 01:29:41.293
No!

1021
01:29:44.713 --> 01:29:51.220
SNIPER: NO NATION

1022
01:30:07.611 --> 01:30:08.612
Hello. Brandon.

1023
01:30:20.624 --> 01:30:22.209
You set us up. traitor!

1024
01:30:26.130 --> 01:30:29.424
How many more lives do you think
you have. Brandon Beckett?

1025
01:30:30.759 --> 01:30:32.845
These ropes won't hold me forever.

1026
01:30:34.221 --> 01:30:35.806
I'll be free.

1027
01:30:35.889 --> 01:30:36.974
And when it is.

1028
01:30:38.517 --> 01:30:40.352
I'm going to finish you off. Thabo Zondi.

1029
01:30:49.528 --> 01:30:50.779
This is my revenge!

1030
01:30:54.992 --> 01:30:57.035
